    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Peel</strong> and finely chop (or grate) the garlic</p>\r\n<p><strong>Peel</strong> (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and finely chop (or grate) the ginger</p>\r\n<p><strong>Chop</strong> the coriander finely, including the stalks</p>\r\n<p><strong>Chop</strong> the spring onion<span class=\"text-danger\">(s)</span> finely, discarding the root ends</p>",
